I drill into myself daily to stay forward focused, to not look back not even for a quick glance, to keep pushing towards the future. But, as the end of the year draws close, I can’t help but think back to this time last year. How different things were. My housemate used to laugh and call me ‘ms robe’, as I would sit there for hours overnight working away in my little pink dressing gown. Little to no one knew my name but I was focused and determined. Fast forward to today, this end of year @cartier treat has been well worth it. Christmas has come early 💫
